F00:0020       *     P  PRINT/PUNCH DUMP
F00:0021       *     R  DISPLAY CONTENTS OF TARGET STACK
F00:0022       *          CC   B   A   X   P   S
F00:0023       *     S  1,SET SPEED FOR 10 CPS
F00:0024       *        3,SET SPEED FOR 30 CPS
F00:0025       *     B  PRINT OUT ALL BREAKPOINTS
F00:0026       *     C  CONTINUE EXECUTION FROM CURRENT LOCATION
F00:0027       *     N  NEXT INSTRUCTION
