               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFF9B7:  FF A0 0C
F00:0332       *
F00:0333       * MAIN COMMAND/CONTROL LOOP
F00:0334       *
F00:0335       CONTRL EQU    *
F00:0336       *
F00:0337       * RESTORE STACK POINTER REGISTER
F00:0338       *
