               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB43:  CE A0 80
F00:0672              BSR    PUNT2
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB46:  8D 29
F00:0673              BSR    PUNT2
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB48:  8D 27
