               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB4F:  7A A0 78
F00:0678              BNE    PUN32
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB52:  26 F9
F00:0679              STX    TW
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB54:  FF A0 80
