               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB57:  53
F00:0681              PSHB
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB58:  37
F00:0682              TSX
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB59:  30
F00:0683              BSR    PUNT2    PUNCH CHECKSUM
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB5A:  8D 15
