               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB73:  7E F8 BF
F00:0697       *
F00:0698       * SWI-1 SOFTWARE INTERRUPT LEVEL 1 PROCESSING
F00:0699       *
F00:0700       SWI15  EQU    *
F00:0701              STS    SP       SAVE USER'S SP
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFB76:  BF A0 10
F00:0702       *
F00:0703              LDAA   #3
