               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBA0:  BD FA E2
F00:0740       CTRL   JMP    CONTRL   RETURN TO CONTROL LOOP
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBA3:  7E F9 BA
F00:0741       *
F00:0742       * TRACE INTERRUPT HANDLER
