               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBD1:  8D 70
F00:0776              TSTA            CHECK FOR BRANCH
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBD3:  4D
F00:0777              BPL    CKOBRA   CHECK FOR OTHER THAN BRANCH
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBD4:  2A 35
F00:0778       *
F00:0779       * RELATIVE BRANCH TYPE INSTRUCTION
F00:0780       * DETERMINE WHERE TO PUT SWI
F00:0781       * S- HOLDS POINTER TO USER STACK AFTER SWI
F00:0782              PULA            GET CONDITION CODE
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBD6:  32
F00:0783              DES             UPDATE STACK POINTER AFTER PULL
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBD7:  34
