F00:0811              RTI             TRACE ANOTHER INSTR
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBFC:  3B
F00:0812       *
F00:0813       * X NEEDS TO BE DECREMENTED (OFFSET NEGATIVE)
F00:0814       *
F00:0815       BRGODC DEX             DECREMENT ADDRESS
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBFD:  09
F00:0816              INCA            INCREMENT COUNTER
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFBFE:  4C
