               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFC28:  C1 8D
F00:0847              BEQ    BRGO     (BRANCH PROCESSING)
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFC2A:  27 B6
F00:0848       *
F00:0849       * NOT A BRANCH, JUMP. RTI, RTS
F00:0850       * A REGISTER HOLDS # BYTES IN INSTRUCTION
