               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFC35:  EE 01
F00:0865              BRA    BRG2     GO TRACE NEXT INSTR.
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFC37:  20 B4
F00:0866       *
F00:0867       * RTI ENCOUNTERED
F00:0868       *
