               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFDFD:  7E FF 6F
F00:1229       STARTV BRA    STARTF
               S01:FFFFFFFFFFFFFE00:  20 24
F00:1230       *
F00:1231       * GETFILE LOOKS FOR:
F00:1232       *     1)  A START SEQUENCE
F00:1233       *     2)  A HEADERECORD TYPE
