F00:1790       *                      CONTROL LOOP INITIALIZE
F00:1791       *  EXORTAPE RAM
F00:1792       *AUXILIARY REGISTER STORAGE
F00:1793       FIDH   DS    1
F00:1794       FIDL   DS    1
F00:1795       STARTP DS    1
F00:1796       STOPPG DS    1
F00:1797       TOTCNT DS    1        WINDOW WIDTH
F00:1798       PATDEL DS    1        PATTERN-ELEMENT LENGTH
F00:1799       CL     DS    1        CHECK/LOAD SUB
F00:1800       CLL    DS    1
F00:1801       CLLL   DS    1        RTS
